  "mixStrategy": "Three-layer frequency separation: Synth Bass anchors the low end (MIDI 36-48, C2-C3) with slow root notes, Warm Pad fills the harmonic middle (MIDI 53-67, F3-G4) with sustained open voicings changing every 8-16 seconds, and Vibraphone floats gentle arch-shaped melodies in the upper register (MIDI 62-77, D4-F5). All layers follow the same Dm dorian progression: Dm (0-16s) \u2192 Bb (16-24s) \u2192 C (24-32s) \u2192 Bb (32-40s) \u2192 Dm (40-45s). Note density kept sparse (2-4 new notes per 4 seconds) with long durations (2-8s) ensuring no more than 4-5 simultaneous voices. Energy arc rises gently from 0.3 to 0.6 at the midpoint then settles back to 0.3. Hip-hop flavor expressed through minor pentatonic/dorian color tones and i\u2192bVI\u2192bVII harmonic movement, never through rhythmic intensity.",
